parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden stalling of the engine can cause a loss of power, leading to a loss of control, accidents, or leaving the driver stranded in traffic, which can be dangerous.
symptoms: the vehicle stalls at highway speeds
the vehicle stalls when shifting gears
the vehicle stalls without warning lights or messages.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to a loss of control, accidents, or leaving the driver stranded in traffic, which can be dangerous.
symptoms: The transmission hesitates or fails to shift
the vehicle stalls when shifting gears
the engine stalls when attempting to shift from 1st to 2nd gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the drive shaft can cause loss of control, accidents, or leave the driver stranded, which can be dangerous.
symptoms: The drive shaft falls out of the vehicle while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sunroof drainage system can cause water to flood the interior of the vehicle, creating a hazardous driving condition, and potentially leading to accidents or electrical system failures.
symptoms: Water leaks into the vehicle through the sunroof
water runs down the driver and passengers
no warning signs or indicators prior to the failure.
